title: Cascading Parameter Values Not Displayed Properly in HTML Viewer
description: Cascading parameter values cannot be displayed correctly in the HTML viewer.
OB: When selecting the first parameter value, the second parameter value in the same cascading parameter group is not displayed in the HTML viewer.
EB: When the first parameter value is selected, we expect the second parameter value in the same cascading parameter group to be displayed in the HTML viewer.
SR:
To reproduce this issue, follow these steps:
1. Open the HTML viewer.
2. Select the first parameter value in a cascading parameter group.
